#

Honeycrisp Apple Cider

40 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

BeverageFallEasySweet

Description

A refreshing, sweet, and slightly tart drink perfect for fall or any season!

Ingredients

  • honeycrisp apples: 6-8
  • water: 4 cups
  • brown sugar: 1/2 cup
  • cinnamon sticks: 2
  • whole cloves: 5
  • nutmeg (optional): 1/4 teaspoon
